        <Parent_String>rooms and spaces by property [300082039], rooms and spaces [300133704], built work divisions [300072553], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
